ic properties at high-$z$, as well as to the\norigin of globular clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2016 21:00:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Nov 2016 10:32:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-04"}
