 granular friction.\nSurprisingly, once the limit cycle is reached, the Mohr-friction seem to be\ninsensitive to polydispersity as has been recently reported.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2016 00:51:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2017 04:15:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-19"}
