istribution function lead to\nsolutions of the Liouville equation which relax in time to a steady-state,\nspherically symmetric configuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2016 05:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Mar 2017 17:44:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-19"}
